  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Bootnodes (Profile -> Bootnodes) are being enabled when development mode is turned ON. It happens only on iOS, Android works fine.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nBootnodes are not enabled when dev mode is ON. They can be enabled only by a user switching the \"bootnodes enabled\" toggle.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nBootnodes are enabled when dev mode is ON.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status on iOS \r\n- Go to Profile\r\n- Turn on dev mode\r\n- Open Bootnodes settings\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly, 15 June\r\n* Operating System: iOS\r\n",
